claim.claim-text:
35. A household dishwasher, comprising:
a dishwasher cavity having a dishwasher interior for processing items to be washed;
an air outlet designed to blow out dishwasher interior air of the dishwasher cavity;
a conveying element responsible for blowing out dishwasher interior air;
an air duct leading from the dishwasher cavity to the conveying element; and
an outlet duct extending between the conveying element and the air outlet, said outlet duct designed with a reduced cross-section with respect to the air duct.
